
/* ----------------- pacc_r_autosys_set_ONHOLD ----------------- */

command: $SCRIPT_DIR/autosys_event.pl $SCRIPT_DIR/status_env.csh JOB_ON_HOLD $INPUT/ERP_jobs_07112008.txt

owner: prodacc@usfkl21as210v
permission: wx,mx,me
date_conditions: 0
description: "Sets pacc jobs ON_HOLD for Autosys 4.5 upgrade"
std_out_file: ">$LOGDIR/pacc_r_autosys_set_ONHOLD_`date +%m%d`.log"
std_err_file: ">$LOGDIR/pacc_r_autosys_set_ONHOLD_`date +%m%d`.err"
alarm_if_fail: 0
profile: "/home/prodacc/auto.profile.forcast"
alarm_if_terminated: 0
